; スタート～森の中の廃屋攻略



;■プロローグ１・赤いネックレス探索

;◇イベント01・森の中の廃屋へ潜入
*cottage_1

@saveon
@wait time=800
[texton w=0]
[テオ f=05]「Is this the place we need to investigate...?」[k]
[マックス f=01]「It's where the client said the bandits were lurking!」[k]
I was standing at the entrance of an abandoned house with my friend Max.[k]
We received a request in town and came to this abandoned house to accomplish it.[k]
The quest is to retrieve the client's precious [b]red necklace[/b].[k]
It was stolen by the bandits who have gone to ground here.[k]
To be honest, the reward isn't great, but since we accepted it, we're obliged to complete the request.[k]
As new adventurers, we have no future unless we start off with trivial work.[k]
[テオ f=06]「It's so quiet...」[k]
[マックス f=10]「Please don't let strong monsters appear.」[k]
[textoff]
@call target=*tutorial_1
@wait time=200
[texton w=0]
[マックス f=01]「According to our information, the bandits are lurking on the [b]2nd floor[/b].」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I see.」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Let's go, [テオ]. The sooner we get rid of them, the sooner we can go back to town.」[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇チュートリアル・ダンジョン移動
*tutorial_1

@question title="Would you like to hear the exploration tutorial?"
@return cond='! tf.result'

[texton w=1]
Dungeons are navigated in 3D view.[r]
Use a mouse, keyboard, or gamepad to move.[k]
Move with up and down, and turn with left and right.[r]
Use the Home / End keys or the 5th and 6th buttons on the gamepad to move horizontally (by default).[k]
@image layer=0 storage=tutorial01 left=0 top=0 opacity=255 visible=true
When using the mouse, first move the cursor over the[r]dungeon screen.[r]
The [b]cursor changes[/b] depending on the position of the mouse, so left-click to move / turn.[k]
@image layer=0 storage=tutorial02 left=450 top=310 opacity=255 visible=true
You can also display the [b]operation board[/b] on the screen. You can set this in the [b]System Settings[/b] menu.[k]
@layopt layer=0 visible=false left=0 top=0
The menu is displayed by [b]right-clicking[/b], pressing[r]the [b]ESC key[/b], or the [b]second button[/b] on a gamepad.[r]On it you can do various things such as saving and checking status.[k]
Anywhere you walk is recorded on the [b]map[/b].[r]
Make sure to check the map frequently so you don't get lost.[k]
[textoff]
@return


;◇チュートリアル・戦闘解説
*tutorial_2

@wait time=500
[texton]
[if exp='! game.isFreeMode']
	[マックス f=12]「Ahhh! Wow, enemies!」[k]
	[マックス f=28]「[テオ]! Let's give them a kicking!」[k]
	[テオ f=06]「Understood.」[k]
[endif]
[nw][b]About battle[r]
Combat is menu based.[r]
Select a command, then a target.[r]
You win when all enemies are defeated.[k]
[nw][b]You can select targets with the keyboard or mouse.[r]
Note that if a monster is hard to click on, you can [b red]turn the mouse wheel[b] to temporarily hide monsters in front of it.[k]
[textoff]
@wait time=300
[beventoff]


;◇チュートリアル・アイテム画面解説
*tutorial_3

@question title="View item screen tutorial?" cancel=true
[eventoff cond='! tf.result']

@bg f=tutorial03
[c]
[texton w=1 top=400]
The item screen is where you can interact with items.[r]
Here you can use, move, and equip items.[r]
The left is the [b]equipment area[/b], and the right is[r]the item [b]storage area[/b].[r]
The [b]party area[/b] below is used for handing items.[k]
All operations are done by drag and drop or using the[r]keyboard.[r]
You can move an item to any location by dragging and[r]dropping[/b] with the mouse.[k]
If you use the keyboard, grab the item with the [b]Enter[r]button[/b], move it with the direction keys, and press the[r][b]Enter button[/b] again to place it.[k]
[textoff]

@bg f=tutorial04
[c]
[texton w=1]
If you drop an item into the equipment area on the left,[r]the character will [b]equip it[/b], if possible.[r]
If you grab the equipment that the character is wearing, you can take it off.[k]
If you drop an item in the party area below, you will [b]hand it to that character[/b] unless their storage area is full.
 [k]
[textoff]

@bg f=tutorial05
[c]
[texton w=1]
Each item will show a menu if you right-click [b]with[r]the mouse[/b] or press the [b]option button[/b] (by default, the[r]space key or the third button on the gamepad).[r]
Use / delete items here.[r]
It also shows details about the item.[k]
This performs the same operation using an item in[r]battle would.[r]
You can also use an item by double-clicking the [b]left[r]mouse button[/b].[k]
You can collect items from treasure chests, repair items,[r]and appraise them, so please master this item screen.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

@gameon
[texton w=0]
If you're unsure, try dragging and dropping stuff onto characters.[r]I think you'll be able to work it out.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント02・捕まったマリアとリーゼル
*cottage_2

; 廃屋の一室
@wait time=500
@fg l=thief_blue_fight1 left=192 b
@fg a=リーゼル e=ローブ・後ろ手 left=374 f=18 b
@fg c=マリア e=後ろ手 left=640 f=07 b
@fg r=thief_green_fight1 left=780
@wait time=500
[texton w=1]
[？？？ v=vl001 key=リーゼル f=18 buf=9]「Eek...!」[k]
[？？？ v=va001 key=マリア f=07 buf=10]「Hey! Let go!」[k]
[男 f=thief_green_01]「These women... they seem to be adventurers. Did someone send you here?」[k]
[男 f=thief_blue_01]「Well, since you've wandered into our hideout, we can't just let you leave!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
When I looked into the room, there were several rough looking men in the corner.[k]
The men surround two girls, who'd been tied up.[k]
What are they doing? Are they-?[k]
[少女 key=マリア v=va002 f=07 buf=10]「You guys are bandits! Bothering the townsfolk is unforgivable!」[k]
@fg a=リーゼル left=374 f=09
[少女 key=リーゼル v=vl002 f=09 buf=9]「Maria...」[k]
; ↑ 心細そうに
[盗賊 f=thief_blue_01]「...Cheeky woman. She seems to need to understand her position.」[k]
With that said, one man put his hand on the one called Maria's shirt.[k]
@se f=tear
@flash on
@fgf c=マリア e="上半身裸・後ろ手" left=640 f=51
@flash off=500
∗rrrippp!∗[k]
[マックス e=現在の装備 f=21]「Oh...!」[k]
The thief ripped off Maria's shirt by force![k]
Her plump breasts bounce out![k]
@fgf c=マリア left=640 f=37
[マリア v=va003 f=37]「Kyaa!」[k]
@fg a=リーゼル left=374 f=11
[少女 key=リーゼル v=vl003 f=11 buf=9]「Maria!」[k]
[盗賊 f=thief_blue_01]「Oh wow! You've got great tits, huh?」[k]
@fgf c=マリア left=640 f=28
[マリア v=va004 f=28]「Damn you...!」[k]
The men's eyes all turn to Maria's bare breasts. Her face turns bright red and she glares tearfully at the men.[k]
[盗賊 f=thief_blue_01]「Those boobs make committing another crime seem tempting.」[k]
@fg a=リーゼル left=374 f=09
[少女 key=リーゼル v=vl004 f=09 buf=9]「Stop... don't do anything terrible to Maria...」[k]
[盗賊 f=thief_green_01]「Oh, I'll also love you a lot later.」[k]
With that said, a man reaches for the other girl, and strokes his hand over her clothes.[k]
@fg a=リーゼル left=374 f=17
[少女 key=リーゼル v=vl005 f=17 buf=9]「N-no...」[k]
[マリア v=va005 f=28]「Stop! Don't touch Riselle!」[k]
[盗賊 f=thief_blue_01]「You still don't get it. You're in no position to tell us anything.」[k]
[盗賊 f=thief_green_01]「Oh yeah, there's two pussies to share now! You're gonna be fucked and panting together!」[k]
@fg a=リーゼル left=374 f=09
[リーゼル f=09]「...!」[k]
[マリア v=va006 f=28]「Damn...! Who would... with guys like you!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...!」[k]
Maria struggles desperately to escape her restraints. But with her arms tied behind her back, she can't do anything.[k]
On the other hand, the girl named Riselle just shook with fear.[k]
At this rate, both of them will be raped by these men.[k]
@cl b
@fg c=テオ f=05
[テオ f=05]「Oi! Let them go!」[k]
[盗賊 f=thief_blue_02]「...!」[k]
[盗賊 f=thief_green_02]「Huh? Who are you guys?」[k]
I jump into the room. The men's eyes immediately turned to me.[k]
[リーゼル f=05]「...!」[k]
[マリア v=va007 f=51]「What...? Help came...?」[k]
@fg r=マックス f=12
[マックス f=12]「Hey [テオ]... Is that sensible? There's more of them than us, right?」[k]
Max entered the room with this anxious question.[k]
[テオ f=05]「I've got to help them. Max, fight with me.」[k]
@fg r=マックス f=09
[マックス f=09]「...I dunno about this, but okay.」[k]
@cl b
@fg c=thief_blue_fight2 b
@fg l=thief_blue_fight2 b
@fg r=thief_green_fight2
[盗賊 f=thief_green_02]「What, you bastards feeling pumped up?」[k]
All the men surrounding Maria turn round.[k]
Weapons in hand, they approach me and Max.[k]
[盗賊 f=thief_blue_02]「Dumb wannabe heroes. We'll cut you apart!」[k]
