; 盗賊たちと戦闘
@monster pos=1 name=ローグ
@monster pos=2 name=ローグ
@monster pos=3 name=ハイウェイマン
@monster pos=4 name=ローグ
@monster pos=5 name=ローグ
@callbattle bgm=boss escape=false gameover=true
@eval exp='game.party.minimumRecovery()'

; 戦闘に勝利
[texton w=0]
[盗賊 f=thief_blue_02]「These guys are pretty strong! Time for a quick retreat!」[k]
We were able to win the battle with the bandits. Perhaps realizing they were outmatched, they fled all at once.[k]
[マックス f=09]「Phew, I was pretty worried there, but we managed to win.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「I have to help them.」[k]
First I'll cut Maria's restraints.[k]
[マックス f=01]「Are you hurt?」[k]
[マリア v=va008 f=10]「No, I'm okay...」[k]
[マックス f=22]「A-anyway, you've got big tits, huh?」[k]
[マリア v=va009 f=27]「Hey! Don't look! Pervert!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Are you okay too?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl006 f=26]「Y-yeah...」[k]
Next is Riselle. Her body was still quivering with fear.[k]
...Not only is she quiet, she's also thin and delicate. Why is this girl working as an adventurer?[k]
Anyway... up close, she's quite pretty...[k]
[テオ f=02]「Okay, the rope's untied.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl007 f=26]「T-thank you...」[k]
[テオ f=25]「...！ ∗badump∗」[k]
Riselle's trembling eyes hold my own.[k]
...My heart beat faster. Of course, she's just thanking me for helping her.[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=マリア e="通常" left=378 f=02 b
@fg r=リーゼル e="ローブ,革のブーツ" left=640 f=26
[texton w=1]
[マリア v=va010 f=02]「You guys are pretty strong, you really helped out.」[k]
Maria, who changed into a replacement shirt, thanks us.[k]
[マックス f=03]「What a mess!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「By the way, why are you here?」[k]
[マリア v=va011 f=02]「Oh, we were asked to recover a red necklace that was stolen from a tavern in Bravetown.」[k]
[マックス f=05]「Isn't that the same as our quest?!」[k]
[マリア v=va012 f=14]「I found the whereabouts of the thieves, but then I messed up.」[k]
Maria says, sticking out her tongue.[k]
[テオ f=05]「So you were caught...」[k]
[マリア v=va013 f=02]「Hey, you guys came here because of the same request, right?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Ah, yeah...」[k]
[マリア v=va014 f=02]「The thieves showed the necklace off earlier, so it should be over there?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「I see! Okay, I'll look for it... But is that okay? You both had the same request.」[k]
[マリア v=va015 f=02]「...We ended up needing to be rescued, so you can have it. We'll fail our request, but I'm grateful we can return safely. That's fine right, Riselle?」[k]
[リーゼル f=26]「...∗nod∗」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Thank you. Then please be patient while I find the necklace.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
[eventoff]


;◇イベント03・ネックレス発見
*cottage_3

; 廃屋の一室
[texton]
[マックス f=01]「Hey, [テオ]. Isn't this the necklace that the client wanted?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Probably.」[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=マリア left=378 f=02 b
@fg r=リーゼル e="ローブ" left=640 f=26
[texton w=1]
[マリア v=va016 f=02]「It looks like you found what you're looking for. Well then, let's go, Riselle.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl008 f=26]「Y-yeah...」[k]
[マックス f=09]「Yes, let's go.」[k]
[マリア v=va017 f=01]「See ya! Thanks for your help, you guys!」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
[texton w=0]
Maria and Riselle left.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
A two girl party...[k]
While female adventurers aren't uncommon, having a party of just two young girls seems dangerous.[k]
Maria looked the adventuring type, but timid Riselle was the complete opposite.[k]
I'm a little worried... Are they really going to carry on working as adventurers?[k]
[マックス f=33]「That Maria was a cute dwarf. You should have invited her to join our party!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Now we've finished the job, let's go back to town.」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Right, feels like we've been here forever.」[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]
